---
import boschLogo from "../../assets/boschLogo.png";
import huaweiLogo from "../../assets/huaweiLogo.png";
import bshLogo from "../../assets/bshLogo.png";
import teduLogo from "../../assets/teduLogo.png";
import michael from "../../assets/michael.gif"
---



<div
  class="relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center overflow-hidden h-auto bg-gray-900 py-12 pb-4 md:py-12 lg:py-36 sm:p-12 min-[320px]:p-4 lg:pt-12 animate-fade-in"
>
<div class="flex justify-center animate-fade-in">
  <img src={michael.src} alt="" class="w-96 h-auto md:w-96 md:h-auto" />
</div>
<br/><br/>
  <h2
    class="text-5xl min-[320px]:text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white light:text-white"
  >
    Experience
  </h2>
  
  <ol
    class="items-center w-10/12 relative border-l border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
  >
    <li class="mb-10 ml-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>

      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >January 2023</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center text-xl font-semibold text-white dark:text-white"
      >
        Software Engineer at <img
          src={boschLogo.src}
          alt="Bosch Logo"
          class="h-auto w-1/5 m-2 ml-4 grayscale-icon min-[320px]:w-1/3 md:w-1/4 lg:w-1/7"
        />
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Contributed to the web applications of BMG/ENG-8TR, a cutting-edge
        diesel engine technology designed to enhance engine efficiency and
        reduce emissions.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Utilizing Angular, RxJS, Nx applications, and .NetCore technologies,
        have worked in fast-paced and agile teams on a global scale.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Gained an understanding of the critical role of software in driving
        advancements in diesel engine technology, learned the importance of
        developing innovative solutions that can help address environmental
        challenges while delivering value to customers.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-blue-700 focus:z-10 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-200 focus:text-blue-700 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-400 dark:border-gray-600 dark:hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-700"
        >Learn more <svg
          class="w-3 h-3 ml-2"
          aria-hidden="true"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 14 10"
        >
          <path
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
        </svg></a
      >
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>
      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >June 2022</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold text-white dark:text-white"
      >
        Frontend/Cloud Engineer <img
          src={huaweiLogo.src}
          alt="Huawei Logo"
          class="h-auto w-1/5 m-2 ml-4 grayscale-icon min-[320px]:w-1/3 md:w-1/4 lg:w-1/7"
        />
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Developed website for advertising Huawei Cloud, using VueJS and
        TypeScript.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Designing, developing, and deploying modular cloud-based systems.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Developed international websites using Vue 3 + TypeScript, Vue 2, Vuex
        ReactJS and NodeJS. I have experienced testing web applications using
        jest, e2e testing.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Collaborating with development teams to evaluate and identify optimal
        cloud solutions.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>
      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >February 2022</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold text-white light:text-white"
      >
        Power Platform Developer <img
          src={bshLogo.src}
          alt="BSH Logo"
          class="h-auto w-1/12 m-2 ml-4 bsh-icon min-[320px]:w-1/4 md:w-1/6 lg:w-1/6"
        />
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Developed PowerApps, Power Automate and SharePoint applications.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Gained experience in agile software development while working with
        global teams.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

<div
  class="relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center overflow-hidden h-auto bg-gray-900 py-12 pt-0 md:py-24 lg:py-72 sm:p-12 min-[320px]:p-4 lg:pt-0 animate-fade-in"
>
  <h2
    class="text-5xl font-bold text-white light:text-white min-[320px]:text-3xl sm:text-4xl"
  >
    Education
  </h2>
  <ol
    class="items-center w-10/12 relative border-l border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
  >
    <li class="ml-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>

      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >September 2019 - January 2024</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold text-white light:text-white"
      >
        B.Sc. Computer Engineering <img
          src={teduLogo.src}
          alt="BSH Logo"
          class="grayscale-icon h-auto w-1/12 m-2 ml-4 bsh-icon min-[320px]:w-1/6 md:w-1/6 lg:w-1/12"
        />
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Took fundamental courses of programming, data structures, algorithms,
        OOP, software engineering, computer architecture, operating systems,
        computer networks, database management systems.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Web Development Team member of Google Developer Student Clubs. Gave
        introductory training to GIT which its language is Turkish for the
        students, via the online platform YouTube <span
          ><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6A4dPWhVScI">(link)</a
          ></span
        >.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-zinc-50 dark:text-gray-400">
        Wrote article for Analysis of Algorithms course. The article is about
        Graph theories and performance comparison of Dijkstra, Bellman-Ford and
        Floyd-Warshall algorithms.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 1s ease-in-out forwards;
    opacity: 0; /* Initial opacity set to 0 */
  }
  .grayscale-icon {
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    transition: filter 0.25s ease-in-out;
  }

  /* Remove the grayscale filter on hover */
  .grayscale-icon:hover {
    filter: none;
  }
</style>
